  "Description": "MUSE — Modular Unreal Studio Engine, by Prysma Studio. Lets AI assistants (Claude, Cursor, etc.) work alongside the Unreal editor via the Model Context Protocol. 200+ automation actions for assets, actors, levels, blueprints, animation, materials and more, served by a native in-editor MCP server. Based on ChiR24/Unreal_mcp (MIT).",
